  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House", 
    "date": "2018-03-06T05:00:00Z", 
    "text": "Local Taxpayer Protection Act of 2018 \n\nThis bill requires certain hydropower facility licensees to make an annual payment of $1.8 million to the county in which the licensed hydropower facility is located. Subsequent payments must increase by 2% of the preceding annual payment.\n\nThe fee applies to a state, or a subdivision of the state, that (1) received a license for a pumped-storage facility, and (2) filed for the license in April 2017."
  }, 
